  "texts": [
    "These results were not maintained at the follow-up evaluations in the exercise groups, which demonstrated a significant increasing trend in sedentary time at 6 months (∆ m3-m2 HIIT 141.4 ± 127.9 min/day, p < 0.001 and ∆ m3-m2 MICT 86.0 ± 75.6 min/day, p < 0.001) and also at 12 months (∆ m4-m2 HIIT 144 ± 151.6 min/day, p < 0.001 and ∆ m3-m2 MICT 50.0 ± 88.0 min/day, p < 0.001), but this results remains lower than prior to participating in community-based exercise CR programs.",
    "In PA levels at 6 and 12 months, MICT maintained the amount of LPA from post intervention, but MVPA decreased significantly.",
    "The same was observed in the HIIT group with a decreasing trend in LPA and MVPA.",
    "The control group had a decrease in all PA indicators at 6 and 12 months of follow-up evaluations (Fig. 5).",
    "Significant differences were observed between the exercise groups and the control group in sedentary time, MVPA and number of steps (p < 0.001) over time."
